folder: East 168th Street & Washington to Third Avenues., Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: East 168th Street - Washington to Third Avenues.
text:
East 169th Street (right), north side, east from and including Washington, to and including Third Ave. Also shown (left) are Nos. 1294 and 1296 Washington Ave., at and adjoining the N.E. corner of East 169th Street.

May 24, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.
